@node "Document_5" "History"
@{b}History@{ub}

Changes since Version 1.1 (first Aminet release November 1997)

Version 1.2 (second Aminet release 21Dec97)

1.   Date routines re-written.  Cal no longer uses OS date functions.  As
     a result, Cal should work with any version of WorkBench. (18Dec97)
@endnode

